{"tid":2042181,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"OKTA 幫人儲存密碼都1800億?","createTime":"2020-05-29T17:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T05:33:40.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1a84ea17e719f46c14ac4204e5170183feead2","tid":2042181,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">本文經刪減<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n先看介紹影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/11SL-NnGp4E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F11SL-NnGp4E&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=8b4bbb29\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/11SL-NnGp4E</a><br />\n<br />\nOkta is a leader in the cloud-based online identity management, a set of tools used to allow access. The company has seen strong growth over the years, driven by technology, strong customer growth and retention, account growth and investment in sales. <span style=\"color: red;\">Okta&rsquo;s technology is rated among the best</span>, as analyzed by Gartner.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2020/5/9/50190104-15890032990725632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.seekingalpha.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F5%2F9%2F50190104-15890032990725632.jpg&h=cd7b49ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對問題:<br />\n1. 估值極高，一旦收入成長下降，股價會大幅下降，甚至只有６０％<br />\n2. 已經競爭對手出現，但OKTA已經同不少大企業建立合作關係<br />\n3. 受惠COVID，WFH令更多人使用<br />\n4. OKTA起同類公司當中最貴，客戶起經濟唔好既時候，通常會推遲購買軟件服務<br />\n<br />\n2020 Q1 Earning Report (2020-05-28)<br />\n收入: $182.9M 46% YOY<br />\n淨虧損: Non-GAAP $8.1M ,上年同季 $21.4M<br />\n現金流: $29.8M ,上年同季 $13.2M<br />\n大公司客戶(100K): 1580 38% YOY<br />\n客戶存留率: 121%<br />\n<br />\n公司預期 2020 Q2<br />\n收入: 185M to $187M  32%-33% YOY<br />\n淨虧損: Non-GAAP $5-4M<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<em>Source:<br />\nOkta: The Risk-Reward Is More Favorable Than You Think @SA</em>"},{"pid":"1d7c991fbf0e6325da02e212c145e9be746d27ca","tid":2042181,"uid":128178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"我公司就係用okta<br />\n係有用但完全唔明佢咁都可以值咁多錢<br />\n技術成本極低，極易被replace"},{"pid":"405e28d2b38a558503731d78ca2b57df1d2f68e7","tid":2042181,"uid":106027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d7c991fbf0e6325da02e212c145e9be746d27ca","tid":2042181,"uid":128178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"我公司就係用okta<br />\n係有用但完全唔明佢咁都可以值咁多錢<br />\n技術成本極低，極易被replace"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:35:00.000Z","msg":"我冇用過 但技術算低咩<br />\n我就咁睇下 要同其他人做partnership 同integration<br />\n例如cyberark 果啲 應該都有市場"},{"pid":"9a7a4976c65f77e1cf17779e611bfd41115deebe","tid":2042181,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d7c991fbf0e6325da02e212c145e9be746d27ca","tid":2042181,"uid":128178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"我公司就係用okta<br />\n係有用但完全唔明佢咁都可以值咁多錢<br />\n技術成本極低，極易被replace"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"我諗呢個係極大部份人既問題,包括我<br />\n不如你講吓平時用有咩特別之處?any bug etc?<br />\n有冇類似軟件?"},{"pid":"11efc092c8a435a38294d5d5fa0c2fbf2364a698","tid":2042181,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"405e28d2b38a558503731d78ca2b57df1d2f68e7","tid":2042181,"uid":106027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d7c991fbf0e6325da02e212c145e9be746d27ca","tid":2042181,"uid":128178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"我公司就係用okta<br />\n係有用但完全唔明佢咁都可以值咁多錢<br />\n技術成本極低，極易被replace"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:35:00.000Z","msg":"我冇用過 但技術算低咩<br />\n我就咁睇下 要同其他人做partnership 同integration<br />\n例如cyberark 果啲 應該都有市場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T18:12:58.000Z","msg":"佢唯一可以繼續搶領導地位就係靠同人PARTNERSHIP <br />\n佢自己個USER BASE 大, 會有